lender.name: acuitybrandscontrolgroup
lender.occupational_info:
Lithonia Controls was founded in 1985, as the controls division of Lithonia Lighting. We were one of the early pioneers in the lighting control market place. In March of 2007 we transformed into Synergy Lighting Controls, an Acuity Brands Company. During the past two decades, we developed a platform of products and solutions. These solutions include: • Synergy®: our industry leading lighting control system that is native BACnet and capable of Power dimming, DALI control, fluorescent dimming and switching integrated into a single system from a single lighting control panel to a multi-building campus network using RS485, fiber optics, Ethernet, or the Internet. • SIMPLY5™ Lighting Intelligence: an integrated lighting solution that includes Lithonia Lighting®, Peerless®, Mark Architectural Lighting™ and Gotham® light fixtures with embedded controls. By adding intelligence to highly efficient lighting fixtures along with Reloc® cabling, SIMPLY5 provides an optimized plug and play lighting solution that is 1-simple to design, 2-simple to install, 3-simple to use, 4-simple to expand and 5-simple to maintain ... thus its name: SIMPLY5. • SwitchPak® relay panel: A cost effective relay panel that provides control of up to 8 lighting circuits. The unique menu driven display is one of the simplest systems to install and set up. SwitchPak® saves up to 25% vs. lighting contactor panels, saves contractor installation time, is easier to use than a time clock, provides an easy way to override lights, meets energy codes and has one of the smallest footprints in the industry. • Litronic® Occupancy Sensors: a full line of Infrared, Ultrasonic and Multi-Technology sensors for energy management. • Wallbox Dimmers that provide smooth full-range dimming of fluorescent fixtures equipped with the Advance Mark 10™ dimming ballasts, Fluorescent four-wire dimming ballasts, Electric Low Voltage dimming ballasts, Magnetic Low Voltage dimming ballasts, and incandescent fixtures.
